<section class="briefings" id="briefings">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">Executive Intelligence</div>
    <h2 class="section-headline reveal">Monthly Executive AI Briefings</h2>
    <div class="briefings-grid">
      <div class="briefings-text reveal">
        <p>AI moves faster than your leadership team can track. By the time you've read the latest report, the landscape has shifted again.</p>
        <p>Each month, I deliver a board-ready briefing on what actually changed in AI, what it means for your industry, and what decisions it forces. No hype, no jargon — just the signal your leadership team needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="briefings-cta reveal">
        <a href="#engage" class="btn-primary">Request a Sample Briefing</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .briefings {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    background: var(--chocolate);
    position: relative;
  }

  .briefings::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
  }

  .briefings-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .briefings-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.85);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .briefings-text p + p { margin-top: 24px; }

  .briefings-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .briefings { padding: 120px 24px; }
    .briefings-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
  }
</style>
